Build:
  make

Usage:
  ./compiler <input.c>

This produces two output files:
  <input>.ll   - optimized LLVM IR
  <input>.s    - x86-32 assembly

To assemble and run:
  clang -m32 <input>.s main.c -o a.out
  ./a.out

Example:
  ./compiler assemblygenerator/assembly_gen_tests/square.c
  clang -m32 assemblygenerator/assembly_gen_tests/square.s assemblygenerator/assembly_gen_tests/main.c -o a.out
  ./a.out
